snippet.title: Suicide Guy - Teaser
snippet.description:
Our new game in development "Suicide Guy"! 
Release date is summer 2017 on Steam.

The game is a first person action puzzle game set in the dreams of the main character (Suicide Guy).
You have to wake up from his dreams, and the only solution is by finding a way to kill yourself.
